### robot-id.eth API — REST collection (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP)
@base = http://localhost:3001
@apiKey = rid_REPLACE_ME

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Tiers + USDC prices
GET {{base}}/auth/tiers

### SIWE → API key (requires an active on-chain subscription)
POST {{base}}/auth/keys/wallet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "0xYourOemAddress",
  "message": "robot-id.eth: issue API key",
  "signature": "0xSignatureOfMessage"
}

### Key info (auth)
GET {{base}}/auth/keys/info
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Read a robot (public)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/robots/1

### Register single (auth) → unsigned tx
POST {{base}}/api/v1/robots
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "0xRobotHolder",
  "serialNumber": "SPOT-0001",
  "manufacturer": "Boston Dynamics",
  "model": "Spot",
  "capabilityClass": "quadruped-inspection",
  "firmwareVersion": 1,
  "locked": false
}

### Preauthorize a batch (auth) → Merkle root + unsigned submitRoot tx
POST {{base}}/api/v1/robots/batch/preauthorize
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "manufacturer": "Unitree",
  "model": "Go2",
  "capabilityClass": "quadruped",
  "locked": false,
  "serials": [
    { "serialNumber": "GO2-0001", "owner": "0x000000000000000000000000000000000000dEaD" },
    { "serialNumber": "GO2-0002", "owner": "0x000000000000000000000000000000000000bEEF" }
  ]
}

### Proof for one serial (public)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/robots/batch/0xBATCH_ID/proof/GO2-0001

### Capability — latest attestations
GET {{base}}/api/v1/capability/1

### Capability — verify proof
POST {{base}}/api/v1/capability/1/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{ "capabilityKey": "max_payload_kg", "leaf": "0x...", "proof": ["0x..."] }

### Submit an AI/voice intent (auth) → unsigned tx
POST {{base}}/api/v1/intent
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "robotId": 1,
  "command": "Authorize payment for charging dock B and log the task",
  "actionTarget": "0xVendor",
  "value": "0",
  "nonce": 1
}

### OTA — verify a firmware signature
GET {{base}}/api/v1/ota/1/verify?firmwareHash=0x...&newVersion=4&signature=0x...&oemAddress=0x...

### Subscription status
GET {{base}}/api/v1/subscription/0xYourOemAddress

### GraphQL
POST {{base}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{ "query": "{ totalMinted subscription(address:\"0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000\"){ active tierName } }" }
